            <title>[LU-3136] test-framework.sh: do_rpc_nodes() is missing some path (i.e. /bin,/usr/sbin)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3136</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;== lnet-selftest test smoke: lst regression test ===================================================== 16:03:23 (1365462203)&lt;br/&gt;
fat-amd-4: /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/functions.sh: line 225: lsmod: command not found&lt;br/&gt;
fat-amd-2: /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/functions.sh: line 225: lsmod: command not found&lt;br/&gt;
